A massive industrial warehouse interior in cyberpunk style, where two enormous server monoliths face each other across a glowing data stream flowing between them like liquid mercury. One monolith is sleek obsidian with blue neon circuitry patterns, the other is weathered brass and copper with exposed gears and steam vents. Between them, thousands of tiny glowing data particles flow in both directions through translucent tubes, merging and separating in the center where they form a swirling vortex. The scene is bathed in contrasting blue and amber light, with holographic data visualizations floating in the air. Rain drips through gaps in the corrugated metal ceiling, creating small puddles that reflect the neon glow. Industrial cables hang like vines throughout the space.
